sc_cat_item.description: The T-Systems Welcome Kit for new joiners is a carefully crafted package designed to make employees feel valued and prepared from day one. This kit includes essential tools, branded merchandise, and key resources to support a smooth transition into the company. New joiners can expect to find items like a laptop, chargers, and headphones for seamless connectivity, along with a notepad, pen, and planner for organization. To welcome employees into the T-Systems culture, the kit also contains company-branded accessories such as a water bottle, tote bag, or hoodie, showcasing the company logo. Additionally, it may include an orientation guide, contact list, and other onboarding materials, offering a comprehensive introduction to T-Systems’ values, culture, and resources. The Welcome Kit is more than just equipment; it’s a warm invitation to feel part of the team and thrive in the new role.
